            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>Snuggled in the heart of the Greenboro/South Keys district, the Diane Deans Greenboro Community Centre opens its doors to welcome all. We offer a wide variety of recreation programs for all ages, stages and interests. There is a state of the art fitness studio, cardio and weight room, group cycling studio, dance and yoga studio, a full sized gymnasium ideal for sports and a variety of multi-purpose rooms. Consider renting our spaces for birthday parties, meetings, sports leagues, and much more. You will also find the Greenboro District Library located within the facility. Outside, just across Lorry Greenberg Drive, there are public tennis courts and walking trails and out back is a large park with more walking trails, sports fields, an amazing play structure, and wading pool. Greenboro Community Centre; it's a great place to be.</p>
